data.description:
This recently updated to this Century 3 Bedroom 2 Bath site built cozy but not too big or not too small home that is located in a very desirable and secluded West Payson neighborhood would be a great starter home or weekend retreat.  What makes it special.
***MOTIVATED SELLER - MAKE OFFER
***Home is MOVE-IN ready with washer, dryer, all major appliances included.  Bring what you have and start living today.  No need to worry about having to purchase those items.
***Home is all Electric with Central Air HVAC, but also has a Wood Burning Stove with Blower if you prefer the coziness of radiant heat from a wood fire. ***Fully fenced private low maintenance back yard with a 16ft x 10ft Shed with Loft that can be used for storage, workshop, or She Shed.  Backyard is large enough to build a Garage if shed is not enough for you.
***This large almost quarter acre lot also has plenty of room for all your toys you have or want with enough room on the side to park that large RV or Trailer anywhere you want.
***The best part is it only located a half mile from Tonto National Park entrance where you can hike, ride your bikes, or drive your ATV's and enjoy all the riding trails Payson has to offer.        
***There have been many upgrades to the property including Kitchen, Bathrooms, Flooring, NEW wood siding and paint, to include the Main Electrical Panel replaced in 2020 with all new Circuit Breakers.
***WHY WOULD YOU WANT ANYTHING MORE.  Come see this gem today before you have to settle for something less.
